{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"336656-picnic-on-grass","title":"Picnic on Grass","description":"Grass can be of different kinds. It can be soft, it can be rough, you can smell it and even taste it.  Best of all is that you can picnic on grass. ","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Venkataraghavan Subha Srinivasan"],"illustrators":["Annada Menon"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/336656-picnic-on-grass"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/474156/size3/d3b59531e7aa166d232530da42547ac8.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/474156/size6/d3b59531e7aa166d232530da42547ac8.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/426480/size6/41f374537938fbb98dfafd6ed5549fce.jpg","text":"You can tumble\nYou can sleep\nYou can roll\nYou can smell","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/426481/size6/631a6e8ecb066de2e40947540884033b.jpg","text":"and you can picnic on grass,\nthat is...\nYou can taste","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/426482/size6/d56f5636dde02f202e872eaeccdca179.jpg","text":"Sweet and juicy like sugarcane","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/426483/size6/1656a4e31ae745bd37b05a4231a83da1.jpg","text":"Lemony and sweet-scented like lemongrass","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/426484/size6/be47164b1a7243937b1d3ff8aec1a27b.jpg","text":"Soft and smooth like munja grass","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/426485/size6/c1611bdd9750649f3e02f166317fa3bb.jpg","text":"Short and tough like Bermuda grass","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/426486/size6/4404918eb321f45634d71b643161e0f1.jpg","text":"Bushy and healthy like Sewan grass","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/426488/size6/94862394cac60abba585404625964761.jpg","text":"Hollow and strong like bamboo","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/426490/size6/382ee60bddc292c552eabe8f75ac653f.jpg","text":"Tall and wavy like elephant grass","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/426491/size6/dd831a5a48f8239ba65fb24f5731b49b.jpg","text":"Deep-rooted and tufty like vetiver","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/426492/size6/d66a7509d4e2631caa7a7cca49406aca.jpg","text":"Munja grass\nAlong riverbanks in North India\nSewan grass\nThe Thar desert\nSugarcane\nThe Deccan Plateau in Central and South India\nLemongrass\nThe Malabar region in northern Kerala\nVetiver grass\nRajasthan, Uttar Pradesh, Karnataka, Tamil Nadu, Kerala and Andhra Pradesh\nElephant grass\nKaziranga National Park, Assam.\nBamboo grass\nNortheast India\nBermuda grass","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":119}}